{
  "stem": "22237.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was ashamed to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was anti-Semitism, but not in such a way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really never experienced that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't really that serious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We kind of took it for granted, but really not much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember that much anti-Semitism when Hitler came in-- before Hitler came in power.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe I felt it a little more because my parents spoke Yiddish, and I was always a little bit ashamed of the fact that they spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were looked down a little bit because of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't know whether it was because they were Jewish or because of their Yiddish language.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- I would-- I have to say that they also learned to speak German later on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was that-- that Yiddish language that made me feel a little bit ashamed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm-- I feel terribly sorry about that now, because in America the Yiddish language is a very respected language, but it wasn't so respected in Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I mentioned before, it was-- wasn't so easy to go to school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in 1935, my parents decided that-- well, there was only my brother and myself at that time visiting school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother had left-- I don't remember, maybe in 1933 already school, because he needed to take a job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Times were getting bad, and he had to bring in a little money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I know that I left school in 1935, mostly because walking to school and coming home was so bad, and my parents were very scared that something would happen to me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they decided to-- not just myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many children would just not continue their education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would just leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We attended, as I mentioned before, this philantropene.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
